title: Forgotten Tomb of the Thunder Bat
story: For a long time the tomb remained deserted. Lately it was squatted by a band of kobolds. It is rumored that Damnon-Menos, a legendary lantern, is still hidden here.

notes.text: A great ironclad door with two keyholes to the east.
A dying kobold, gems among his belongings.
An elegant knight, sitting on the ground.
A bat-shaped key in a box.
A bat-shaped key hidden in a crack of the floor.
